WEBVTT

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:02.800 align:middle line:0
<c.yellow>Go knock at the door.</c>

00:01:07.960 --> 00:01:08.960 align:middle line:0
DOORBELL RINGS

00:01:08.960 --> 00:01:11.960 align:middle line:0
KNOCKING,
SHE PANTS

00:01:15.960 --> 00:01:17.960 align:middle line:-3
Can I help you?
<c.yellow>Ah!</c>

00:01:17.960 --> 00:01:21.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>We've got an appointment</c>
<c.yellow>to see the doctor.</c>

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:22.640 align:middle line:-2
No, you haven't.

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:25.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Yes, we have.</c>
That's impossible.

00:01:25.960 --> 00:01:27.960 align:middle line:-3
The surgery's closed
and has been for some time.

00:01:27.960 --> 00:01:29.960 align:middle line:-2
You'll have to go to Wadebridge.

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:31.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Oh, well... I spoke</c>
<c.yellow>to a Dr Ellingham yesterday.</c>

00:01:31.960 --> 00:01:34.960 align:middle line:-3
No, you didn't.
<c.yellow>Uh, excuse me, yes, I did.</c>

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:38.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I was told to come here</c>
<c.yellow>at 9am this morning, so...</c>

00:01:38.960 --> 00:01:40.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>you're very much mistaken.</c>
BABY GURGLES

00:01:40.960 --> 00:01:42.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>What?</c>

00:01:43.960 --> 00:01:45.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Oh, this is ridiculous.</c>
<c.yellow>My child's here to see the doctor.</c>

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:48.960 align:middle line:-3
I told you -
you'll have go to Wadebridge.

00:01:48.960 --> 00:01:50.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Martin. They're here to see me.</c>

00:01:50.960 --> 00:01:54.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Come in, I'm so sorry.</c>
<c.yellow>Thank you.</c>

00:01:58.960 --> 00:02:00.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>You must be Dr Ellingham.</c>

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:02.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Oh, no, no, I'm not...</c>
She's not a doctor.

00:02:02.960 --> 00:02:04.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>No, I am a qualified</c>
<c.cyan>child counsellor, though.</c>

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Pretty much the same thing,</c>
<c.yellow>isn't it? </c>No, it isn't.

00:02:07.960 --> 00:02:09.960 align:middle line:-3
Why are you so breathless?
<c.yellow>Well, I don't know.</c>

00:02:09.960 --> 00:02:11.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Cos you live at the top of a hill.</c>

00:02:11.960 --> 00:02:14.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Martin, don't you think</c>
<c.cyan>it's about time for her nap?</c>

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:16.960 align:middle line:-2
No. 20 minutes yet.

00:02:16.960 --> 00:02:18.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Aw. What's your name?</c>

00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:19.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Mary.</c>
Mary Elizabeth.

00:02:19.960 --> 00:02:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>She's four months...</c>
Nearly.

00:02:22.960 --> 00:02:25.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>They're so cute at that age.</c>
<c.yellow>Shame it doesn't last, eh?</c>

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:27.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Come through.</c>
<c.yellow>Come on.</c>

00:02:28.960 --> 00:02:30.960 align:middle line:-2
BABY CRIES

00:02:44.960 --> 00:02:48.960 align:middle line:-3
James, the white wheel
goes at the top, not the green.

00:02:48.960 --> 00:02:50.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Thank you.</c>
You're welcome.

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:56.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Sorry for that confusion,</c>
<c.cyan>Martin used to be a doctor.</c>

00:02:56.960 --> 00:02:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, well, he still is,</c>
<c.cyan>he's just not practising any more.</c>

00:02:59.960 --> 00:03:02.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>So we still get people</c>
<c.cyan>regularly knocking at the door,</c>

00:03:02.320 --> 00:03:05.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>expecting the surgery to be open,</c>
<c.cyan>and... and it's not.</c>

00:03:05.960 --> 00:03:07.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Well, I've just moved here,</c>

00:03:07.960 --> 00:03:09.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>so I wouldn't know about</c>
<c.yellow>any of that.</c>

00:03:09.960 --> 00:03:11.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Oh, do you work locally?</c>
<c.yellow>From home.</c>

00:03:11.960 --> 00:03:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Yeah, I run my own</c>
<c.yellow>small graphic design business -</c>

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:18.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>wedding invitations and the like.</c>

00:03:18.960 --> 00:03:21.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Or if you need any business cards,</c>
<c.yellow>I can offer you a good rate.</c>

00:03:21.960 --> 00:03:24.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, I'll bear that in mind.</c>
<c.cyan>So, you must be Dylan.</c>

00:03:24.320 --> 00:03:26.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Are you looking forward</c>
<c.cyan>to starting at the school?</c>

00:03:28.960 --> 00:03:30.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Say hello to the doctor, Dylan.</c>

00:03:30.960 --> 00:03:32.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Erm, no, I'm not a doctor.</c>

00:03:32.960 --> 00:03:36.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I'm Mrs Ellingham, or you can</c>
<c.cyan>call me Louisa if you want.</c>

00:03:37.960 --> 00:03:39.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Look, he's been like this</c>
<c.yellow>for a while.</c>

00:03:39.960 --> 00:03:41.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Moody, withdrawn.</c>

00:03:41.960 --> 00:03:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'm just a bit worried about him,</c>
<c.yellow>aren't I?</c>

00:03:43.960 --> 00:03:49.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I am in the middle of</c>
<c.yellow>a D-I-V-O-R-C-E, so...</c>

00:03:49.960 --> 00:03:51.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Yeah, well, why don't you</c>
<c.cyan>take a seat outside,</c>

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:53.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>and Dylan and I will,</c>
<c.cyan>will have a little chat,</c>

00:03:53.960 --> 00:03:54.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>we'll get to know each other.</c>

00:03:54.960 --> 00:03:59.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>OK. Don't give the nice doctor</c>
<c.yellow>any of your nonsense, all right?</c>

00:04:04.640 --> 00:04:07.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I don't want to sign the petition.</c>
<c.yellow>I just want some cough medicine.</c>

00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:08.960 align:middle line:-2
It's store policy.

00:04:08.960 --> 00:04:10.960 align:middle line:-3
If you want something,
you need to sign.

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:13.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'll go somewhere else, then.</c>
Fine.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:17.960 align:middle line:-3
Don't complain to me if your cough
turns into bronchial pneumonia

00:04:17.960 --> 00:04:19.480 align:middle line:-3
and there's no doctor about
to help you!

00:04:20.800 --> 00:04:21.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Sally.</c>

00:04:21.960 --> 00:04:24.960 align:middle line:-3
Before you purchase your product,
you need to sign the petition.

00:04:24.960 --> 00:04:26.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I don't think</c>
<c.cyan>you should be doing this.</c>

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, it's my shop,
I'm perfectly within my rights.

00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>How many signatures you got?</c>
Every flood starts with a trickle.

00:04:33.960 --> 00:04:35.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Doesn't matter</c>
<c.cyan>if you've got 5,000 signatures,</c>

00:04:35.960 --> 00:04:37.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>you're not gonna change anything.</c>

00:04:37.640 --> 00:04:38.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>The doc's made his decision.</c>

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:40.960 align:middle line:-3
Someone has to change his mind,
then.

00:04:40.960 --> 00:04:42.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>The doc doesn't change his mind.</c>

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:47.960 align:middle line:-3
Cos he's forgotten what it's like
to be out there, saving lives.

00:04:47.960 --> 00:04:48.960 align:middle line:-2
It's the thrill of it all.

00:04:48.960 --> 00:04:50.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>It's not like you can just</c>
<c.cyan>conjure up</c>

00:04:50.960 --> 00:04:53.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>some medical emergency</c>
<c.cyan>out of nowhere.</c>

00:04:53.480 --> 00:04:54.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>You know, maybe it's time to,</c>
<c.cyan>you know...</c>

00:04:54.960 --> 00:04:56.960 align:middle line:-3
Escalate it.
<c.cyan>..let it go.</c>

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:04.960 align:middle line:-3
You're right.
<c.cyan>I am?</c>

00:05:05.960 --> 00:05:06.960 align:middle line:-2
Of course.

00:05:06.960 --> 00:05:08.960 align:middle line:-2
Oh, like you said,

00:05:08.960 --> 00:05:13.960 align:middle line:-3
it's not like I can conjure up
a medical emergency from nowhere.

00:05:15.960 --> 00:05:17.960 align:middle line:-2
You know, bring him to his senses.

00:05:19.640 --> 00:05:21.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>OK. Good.</c>

00:05:21.960 --> 00:05:23.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Good talk.</c>

00:05:34.960 --> 00:05:36.960 align:middle line:-2
For the doctor.

00:05:37.960 --> 00:05:39.960 align:middle line:-2
STAPLE GUN CLICKS

00:05:41.320 --> 00:05:42.960 align:middle line:-2
Ow!

00:05:42.960 --> 00:05:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>These are what we call</c>
<c.cyan>"feeling cards".</c>

00:05:47.960 --> 00:05:49.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Do any of these rabbits here</c>

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:52.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>remind you of how you feel</c>
<c.cyan>about your parents separating?</c>

00:05:52.960 --> 00:05:54.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>I'm not a rabbit.</c>

00:05:55.960 --> 00:05:58.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>No. No, I know you're not.</c>
<c.cyan>It's just...</c>

00:05:58.960 --> 00:06:01.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>this rabbit is happy.</c>

00:06:01.640 --> 00:06:03.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>And this one is angry.</c>

00:06:03.960 --> 00:06:06.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>And look, see, this one is sad.</c>

00:06:08.960 --> 00:06:09.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>I'm eight years old.</c>

00:06:09.960 --> 00:06:13.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>OK. Yeah. No rabbits, then.</c>

00:06:18.960 --> 00:06:20.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>I'm not the problem.</c>

00:06:22.640 --> 00:06:23.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>It's my mum.</c>

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:25.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>What about your mum?</c>

00:06:25.960 --> 00:06:27.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>She's...</c>

00:06:31.640 --> 00:06:34.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>..she's gone weird.</c>

00:06:42.960 --> 00:06:46.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Looks complicated. Probably easier</c>
<c.yellow>just to buy a new one.</c>

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:48.480 align:middle line:-2
Can I help you?

00:06:48.480 --> 00:06:51.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Er, I need a glass of water,</c>
<c.yellow>if that's OK.</c>

00:06:51.960 --> 00:06:52.960 align:middle line:-2
Yes. I'll get it.

00:06:57.800 --> 00:06:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Thank you.</c>
You're welcome.

00:06:59.960 --> 00:07:00.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE COUGHS

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:02.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE RETCHES

00:07:02.960 --> 00:07:04.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE COUGHS

00:07:06.960 --> 00:07:11.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>God. Some folk say that it's rude</c>
<c.yellow>to stare, you know.</c>

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:13.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>What are you doing?!</c>
I'm just checking something.

00:07:13.960 --> 00:07:16.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Get your hands off me!</c>

00:07:16.480 --> 00:07:19.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>It's like her batteries</c>
<c.green>have run out. </c><c.cyan>Mm.</c>

00:07:19.480 --> 00:07:21.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Sometimes she goes to bed</c>
<c.green>before me...</c>

00:07:21.960 --> 00:07:25.000 align:middle line:-3
MUFFLED: <c.yellow>No. I've been having</c>
<c.yellow>difficulty since I walked in here.</c>

00:07:25.000 --> 00:07:27.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>..and she still can't get up</c>
<c.green>in the morning.</c>

00:07:27.960 --> 00:07:30.480 align:middle line:-3
MUFFLED: <c.yellow>..over-stepped your line!</c>
<c.cyan>Sorry, just, er, just a second.</c>

00:07:30.480 --> 00:07:32.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I don't know you, all right?!</c>

00:07:32.960 --> 00:07:35.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Who do you think you are?</c>
<c.yellow>We are strangers.</c>

00:07:35.960 --> 00:07:38.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>But to, sort of, touch me</c>
<c.yellow>and have an opinion on me.</c>

00:07:38.960 --> 00:07:40.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I only came here because of my son.</c>
<c.yellow>And there you are,</c>

00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:42.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>you're staring at me like a weirdo.</c>

00:07:42.960 --> 00:07:44.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Martin? What's going on?</c>

00:07:44.960 --> 00:07:47.160 align:middle line:-3
She was unable to swallow properly.
<c.yellow>He grabbed my face.</c>

00:07:47.160 --> 00:07:49.000 align:middle line:-3
I didn't grab it. I steadied it.
<c.cyan>Right, OK.</c>

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:51.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Martin, I'm with a client. And you</c>
<c.cyan>agreed to stay out the way.</c>

00:07:51.960 --> 00:07:52.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Yeah, I'm so sorry.</c>

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:56.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I can only apologise</c>
<c.cyan>on behalf of myself and Martin.</c>

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:57.960 align:middle line:-2
I've done nothing to apologise for.

00:07:57.960 --> 00:08:00.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Well, sorry, but you should!</c>
<c.yellow>Manhandling me!</c>

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:02.960 align:middle line:-3
You see, you're still struggling
to breathe. <c.green>Doctor!</c>

00:08:02.960 --> 00:08:04.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Oh, Doctor, I've had a mishap!</c>

00:08:04.960 --> 00:08:08.800 align:middle line:-3
No, I-I-I can't treat you,
I'm no longer registered. <c.yellow>See?</c>

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:09.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>You're not actually a doctor!</c>

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:11.960 align:middle line:-3
MARY CRIES
<c.green>I would have gone to Wadebridge,</c>

00:08:11.960 --> 00:08:13.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>but I didn't want to bleed</c>
<c.green>all the way there.</c>

00:08:13.960 --> 00:08:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Martin. Mary.</c>
Yes...

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:17.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>No. I'm with a client.</c>

00:08:17.640 --> 00:08:18.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Fine, I'll go.</c>

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:20.960 align:middle line:-3
Sit there, Mrs Tishell.
<c.green>Yes.</c>

00:08:31.960 --> 00:08:32.960 align:middle line:-2
Oh. Oh, right.

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:35.960 align:middle line:-3
I'll remove the staples
and dress the wound...

00:08:35.960 --> 00:08:37.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>What's wrong with you?</c>
<c.green>Nothing. Nothing's wrong with him.</c>

00:08:37.960 --> 00:08:39.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>It's just a perfectly</c>
<c.green>normal reaction to blood.</c>

00:08:39.960 --> 00:08:41.960 align:middle line:-3
Be quiet. I'm fine.
HE CLEARS THROAT

00:08:41.960 --> 00:08:43.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Sorry.</c>

00:08:45.960 --> 00:08:47.960 align:middle line:-2
WOMAN: <c.yellow>I want you out!</c>

00:08:47.960 --> 00:08:50.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'm fed up with you...</c>
<c.yellow>your bone idleness.</c>

00:08:51.960 --> 00:08:54.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You can take this...</c>
All right, Dad?

00:08:54.960 --> 00:08:57.960 align:middle line:-3
Erm... everything OK?
<c.green>Fine, yes. Great.</c>

00:08:57.960 --> 00:08:59.960 align:middle line:-3
But...
<c.yellow>And this!</c>

00:08:59.960 --> 00:09:02.960 align:middle line:-3
Oh, I'm here to pick up
the champagne. <c.green>Oh, yes, of course.</c>

00:09:02.960 --> 00:09:04.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Maybe it's best you come back</c>
<c.green>a bit later, though.</c>

00:09:04.960 --> 00:09:07.960 align:middle line:-3
Right, because, er...
<c.yellow>Take them... take them all!</c>

00:09:07.960 --> 00:09:09.800 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>And good riddance!</c>

00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:11.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Just a bit of a domestic.</c>

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:14.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>If you wanna apologise,</c>
<c.green>I'll be staying at Al's!</c>

00:09:14.960 --> 00:09:17.640 align:middle line:-3
Er, no, no, that's not
a good idea, Dad.

00:09:17.640 --> 00:09:19.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Put this lot in the van.</c>

00:09:19.960 --> 00:09:23.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I'm going before she starts</c>
<c.green>throwing down the heavy stuff.</c>

00:09:25.640 --> 00:09:26.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>I'm so sorry about Martin.</c>

00:09:26.960 --> 00:09:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>He's the one</c>
<c.yellow>who should be apologising.</c>

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:30.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I'm stressed. You know?</c>

00:09:30.960 --> 00:09:33.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>All I wanted was someone</c>
<c.yellow>to make sure that my son was OK.</c>

00:09:33.160 --> 00:09:35.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I know, and I'd love</c>
<c.cyan>to continue this.</c>

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:37.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Dylan, come on. Hurry up.</c>
<c.cyan>I'll be in touch, then. Yeah?</c>

00:09:37.960 --> 00:09:39.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Come on.</c>

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:40.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE SIGHS

00:09:46.960 --> 00:09:48.960 align:middle line:-2
There. You can go.

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:51.960 align:middle line:-3
If the pain continues
or the bleeding starts again,

00:09:51.960 --> 00:09:54.960 align:middle line:-3
make an appointment in Wadebridge.
<c.green>Thank you, Doctor.</c>

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:57.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>How was it for you?</c>

00:09:57.960 --> 00:09:59.800 align:middle line:-3
How was what?
<c.green>This.</c>

00:09:59.800 --> 00:10:01.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>You seemed to be back</c>
<c.green>in your element.</c>

00:10:01.960 --> 00:10:03.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Maybe you needed something</c>
<c.green>like this</c>

00:10:03.960 --> 00:10:06.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>to remind you</c>
<c.green>of what you've been missing.</c>

00:10:06.960 --> 00:10:08.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Sometimes we all need a little...</c>
Yes. Thank you.

00:10:08.960 --> 00:10:10.960 align:middle line:-3
We're finished here, Mrs Tishell.
<c.green>Going...</c>

00:10:10.960 --> 00:10:12.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>going...</c>

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:16.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Was all that really necessary?</c>

00:10:16.960 --> 00:10:20.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, she was bleeding.
<c.cyan>Not Mrs Tishell. Abigail.</c>

00:10:20.960 --> 00:10:22.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>This is my place of work</c>

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:24.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>and you're picking fights</c>
<c.cyan>with my clients. </c>Well, you saw.

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:27.960 align:middle line:-3
She choked on that water
and her breathing was laboured.

00:10:27.960 --> 00:10:30.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Sounds like you're looking for</c>
<c.cyan>problems that aren't there. </c>I'm not.

00:10:30.960 --> 00:10:34.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>How would you feel if I started</c>
<c.cyan>butting in with your patients?</c>

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:35.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, that's not the same thing,
is it?

00:10:35.960 --> 00:10:38.960 align:middle line:-3
I don't have any patients.
<c.cyan>You don't, no.</c>

00:10:38.960 --> 00:10:39.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>So stop acting like you do.</c>

00:10:39.960 --> 00:10:42.320 align:middle line:-3
Why do we still have
this dog's basket?

00:10:42.320 --> 00:10:44.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Oh, no, don't throw it out.</c>

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>James is still attached to it.</c>
<c.cyan>He still misses Buddy.</c>

00:10:46.960 --> 00:10:48.960 align:middle line:-2
It's been three months.

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:52.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Maybe we should get a new dog.</c>
Absolutely not.

00:10:52.640 --> 00:10:55.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Are you gonna throw it out, then?</c>
I'll do something with it tomorrow.

00:10:55.960 --> 00:10:57.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Anyone might think</c>
<c.cyan>you missed him, too.</c>

00:10:57.960 --> 00:11:00.000 align:middle line:-2
Don't be ridiculous.

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:03.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Erm, sorry, where's all the cutlery?</c>

00:11:03.160 --> 00:11:04.960 align:middle line:-2
Ah. Er, yes.

00:11:04.960 --> 00:11:08.960 align:middle line:-3
I rearranged the drawers to optimise
the usage of space. There.

00:11:08.960 --> 00:11:10.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Doesn't this concern you?</c>

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:12.960 align:middle line:-2
Why, no, it makes more sense.

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:14.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>You were considered one of</c>

00:11:14.960 --> 00:11:16.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>the finest medical minds</c>
<c.cyan>of your generation,</c>

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:19.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>and now you spend your time</c>
<c.cyan>fixing an endless supply of clocks</c>

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>and rearranging things</c>
<c.cyan>that don't need rearranging.</c>

00:11:23.960 --> 00:11:25.000 align:middle line:-2
No, it doesn't concern me.

00:11:25.000 --> 00:11:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, stop it, because it doesn't</c>
<c.cyan>help when I need to prepare lunch.</c>

00:11:28.960 --> 00:11:30.960 align:middle line:-3
I've already prepared lunch.
<c.cyan>Of course you have.</c>

00:11:30.960 --> 00:11:32.960 align:middle line:-2
It's mackerel.

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:34.960 align:middle line:-3
SHE SIGHS
<c.cyan>I know.</c>

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:35.960 align:middle line:-2
Mm-hm.

00:11:53.960 --> 00:11:55.960 align:middle line:-2
All right, I'm off.

00:11:55.960 --> 00:11:58.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Have you finished already?</c>
Yeah.

00:11:58.960 --> 00:12:00.960 align:middle line:-2
Well, I mean... Well, it is five.

00:12:00.960 --> 00:12:03.480 align:middle line:-3
And it's my anniversary, so...
<c.yellow>Of course.</c>

00:12:03.480 --> 00:12:06.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>It's not like we've got</c>
<c.yellow>a mountain of work to be done.</c>

00:12:06.960 --> 00:12:08.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Go on, enjoy yourself.</c>

00:12:08.960 --> 00:12:10.960 align:middle line:-2
I've been here for five months

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:13.960 align:middle line:-3
and you've still got me wearing
a trainee badge.

00:12:13.960 --> 00:12:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Because you've still got</c>
<c.yellow>a lot to learn, young lady.</c>

00:12:15.960 --> 00:12:18.640 align:middle line:-2
Yeah, well, some people might say

00:12:18.640 --> 00:12:20.960 align:middle line:-3
it's just an excuse to pay me
a lower wage.

00:12:20.960 --> 00:12:22.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Well, those people would be wrong.</c>

00:12:22.960 --> 00:12:24.960 align:middle line:-2
PRINTER BEEPS

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:33.960 align:middle line:-2
So, can I get a promotion, then?

00:12:38.960 --> 00:12:40.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Here you are.</c>

00:12:40.480 --> 00:12:43.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Portwenn Paradise Caravan Park.</c>

00:12:43.160 --> 00:12:44.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Fifteen minutes out of town.</c>

00:12:44.960 --> 00:12:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>We've been trying</c>
<c.yellow>to lease it for a while.</c>

00:12:47.960 --> 00:12:50.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You get yourself down there</c>
<c.yellow>tomorrow, get it sorted,</c>

00:12:50.800 --> 00:12:53.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>and we'll, er, see about that badge.</c>

00:12:53.960 --> 00:12:57.320 align:middle line:-2
OK. Thanks.

00:12:58.960 --> 00:12:59.960 align:middle line:-2
Bye.

00:13:02.960 --> 00:13:05.960 align:middle line:-2
TICKING

00:13:28.160 --> 00:13:31.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Martin? I'm just gonna</c>
<c.cyan>settle Mary down.</c>

00:13:31.960 --> 00:13:34.960 align:middle line:-3
Right. Yeah.
I'll be up in a minute.

00:13:34.960 --> 00:13:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Are you OK?</c>
Mm.

00:13:48.960 --> 00:13:50.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>This looks nice.</c>

00:13:52.800 --> 00:13:54.960 align:middle line:-2
Yeah, well...

00:13:54.960 --> 00:13:56.960 align:middle line:-2
We should have gone to a restaurant.

00:13:56.960 --> 00:13:58.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>No. This is perfect, really.</c>

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.960 align:middle line:-2
DOOR SLAMS

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:02.960 align:middle line:-2
Almost perfect.

00:14:02.960 --> 00:14:04.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Dinner, oh, great, I'm famished.</c>

00:14:04.960 --> 00:14:06.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>What are we having?</c>

00:14:06.960 --> 00:14:09.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, we are having our anniversary
dinner, Dad. I did tell you that.

00:14:09.960 --> 00:14:12.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Oh, yes, right. It's just that</c>
<c.cyan>Caitlin normally cooks my meals.</c>

00:14:12.960 --> 00:14:14.960 align:middle line:-3
DOOR OPENS
<c.yellow>Oh. And here's Caitlin.</c>

00:14:14.960 --> 00:14:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I brought the rest of your stuff.</c>
<c.cyan>Just put it over there.</c>

00:14:17.960 --> 00:14:19.960 align:middle line:-3
Dad was just telling me
how much he misses you, Caitlin.

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>No, I said that</c>
<c.cyan>I missed her cooking.</c>

00:14:22.960 --> 00:14:25.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Look, I'm sure this is all</c>
<c.yellow>just a misunderstanding,</c>

00:14:25.160 --> 00:14:26.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>and if you talk about it...</c>

00:14:26.960 --> 00:14:28.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>He's ungrateful. And lazy.</c>

00:14:28.960 --> 00:14:31.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Maybe start with the positives?</c>

00:14:31.960 --> 00:14:32.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>She smothers me.</c>
<c.green>Smothers?!</c>

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:34.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Exactly.</c>

00:14:34.960 --> 00:14:37.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I cook and clean for you.</c>
<c.green>Wash, iron... everything.</c>

00:14:37.960 --> 00:14:39.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I feel trapped,</c>
<c.cyan>like a bird in a cage.</c>

00:14:39.960 --> 00:14:41.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>It's not my fault if you're lazy.</c>

00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:44.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>If it wasn't for me, you wouldn't</c>
<c.green>have a job or a place to sleep.</c>

00:14:44.960 --> 00:14:48.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Al and Morwenna said I can stay with</c>
<c.cyan>them for the foreseeable future.</c>

00:14:48.960 --> 00:14:50.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I don't think we have.</c>

00:14:50.000 --> 00:14:52.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Al and I are gonna go to work</c>
<c.cyan>on his food truck.</c>

00:14:52.960 --> 00:14:54.640 align:middle line:-2
Er, no, we're not.

00:14:54.640 --> 00:14:55.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>He's doing really well,</c>

00:14:55.960 --> 00:14:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>gone from pulling pints</c>
<c.green>to running his own little empire.</c>

00:14:59.960 --> 00:15:01.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>He doesn't want you ruining it!</c>

00:15:01.960 --> 00:15:04.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>With my help and investment, he can</c>
<c.cyan>take things to the next level.</c>

00:15:04.960 --> 00:15:06.320 align:middle line:-2
Er, I'm... I'm fine, Dad, really.

00:15:06.320 --> 00:15:09.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>You don't have anything to invest.</c>

00:15:09.160 --> 00:15:10.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>I've got a nest egg.</c>

00:15:10.960 --> 00:15:12.000 align:middle line:-2
SHE SNIGGERS

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:14.960 align:middle line:-2
What nest egg?

00:15:14.960 --> 00:15:15.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Well, don't you think</c>

00:15:15.960 --> 00:15:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I've been squirrelling away</c>
<c.cyan>money for all these years?</c>

00:15:17.960 --> 00:15:19.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>I just wanted a business to invest.</c>

00:15:19.960 --> 00:15:22.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>And here we are. It's like fate.</c>

00:15:22.320 --> 00:15:24.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>I used to think we were fate, too.</c>

00:15:24.960 --> 00:15:26.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Just shows how wrong you can be.</c>

00:15:28.960 --> 00:15:32.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>So... did, er...</c>
<c.cyan>someone mention dinner?</c>

00:15:35.640 --> 00:15:36.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Ooh!</c>

00:15:41.960 --> 00:15:44.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Morning, Doc.</c>
Yes.

00:15:44.960 --> 00:15:46.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>How's retirement?</c>
I'm not retired.

00:15:46.960 --> 00:15:49.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Oh, you're back at work, then?</c>
No.

00:15:50.960 --> 00:15:53.960 align:middle line:-3
How are you getting on at
the butcher's? <c.yellow>Estate agent.</c>

00:15:53.960 --> 00:15:56.960 align:middle line:-3
That's right, yes.
<c.yellow>Er, yeah, yeah, it's fine.</c>

00:15:56.960 --> 00:15:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I mean, I spend my time behind</c>
<c.yellow>a desk, buried in paperwork,</c>

00:15:59.960 --> 00:16:01.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>with a boss who doesn't</c>
<c.yellow>appreciate my talents, so...</c>

00:16:01.960 --> 00:16:02.960 align:middle line:-2
Right.

00:16:02.960 --> 00:16:04.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>You know...</c>

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:08.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>How's little Mary?</c>
Er, she's tiny.

00:16:09.960 --> 00:16:12.960 align:middle line:-3
Where's your mother?
<c.cyan>She's in the car.</c>

00:16:12.960 --> 00:16:14.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>She says she's too tired</c>
<c.cyan>to do the shopping.</c>

00:16:14.960 --> 00:16:16.960 align:middle line:-2
Hmm. Excuse me.

00:16:23.000 --> 00:16:25.960 align:middle line:-3
Hello!
<c.green>Look at you, perving on people.</c>

00:16:25.960 --> 00:16:27.960 align:middle line:-3
THEY LAUGH
<c.green>That's not right, that is.</c>

00:16:27.960 --> 00:16:29.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>No wonder you got the sack.</c>

00:16:29.000 --> 00:16:31.960 align:middle line:-3
I didn't!
ALL: <c.cyan>Yeah, tosser.</c>

00:16:33.480 --> 00:16:34.960 align:middle line:-2
You were sleeping.

00:16:36.160 --> 00:16:39.960 align:middle line:-3
Open the window.
<c.yellow>I'm fine. I'm fine.</c>

00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:41.960 align:middle line:-3
You don't seem fine.
Let me look at you.

00:16:42.960 --> 00:16:44.960 align:middle line:-2
Let me look at you!

00:16:51.960 --> 00:16:55.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Plenty of people</c>
<c.cyan>take a nap in their car.</c>

00:16:55.160 --> 00:16:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Oh... I'm not sure</c>
<c.cyan>a briefcase is necessary, James.</c>

00:16:59.960 --> 00:17:03.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>You know, most children, they just</c>
<c.cyan>use like a normal bag for school.</c>

00:17:03.960 --> 00:17:05.960 align:middle line:-2
I took a briefcase to school.

00:17:05.960 --> 00:17:07.800 align:middle line:-2
This was no nap.

00:17:07.800 --> 00:17:09.960 align:middle line:-3
When she woke up, she was completely
erratic and disorientated.

00:17:09.960 --> 00:17:13.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Yes. Well, Dylan did say that she,</c>
<c.cyan>erm...</c>

00:17:13.160 --> 00:17:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>she gets tired very easily</c>
<c.cyan>in the evenings.</c>

00:17:15.960 --> 00:17:18.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Do you think there might be</c>
<c.cyan>something seriously wrong with her?</c>

00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:20.960 align:middle line:-3
Yeah, I do. I've been doing
some research on it.

00:17:20.960 --> 00:17:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Yeah. I wondered what that was.</c>
Oh, Ruth.

00:17:22.960 --> 00:17:25.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I need you to water my plants</c>
<c.yellow>while I'm away.</c>

00:17:25.960 --> 00:17:27.960 align:middle line:-2
That's not actually something I do.

00:17:27.960 --> 00:17:29.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Well, now it is.</c>

00:17:29.960 --> 00:17:32.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It's not as though you're busy.</c>

00:17:32.640 --> 00:17:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Ah. Don't look so worried,</c>
<c.yellow>I'll only be in Mexico for a week.</c>

00:17:36.960 --> 00:17:39.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Did you say you're going to Mexico?</c>
<c.cyan>I've always wanted to go there.</c>

00:17:39.960 --> 00:17:42.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Is it for a holiday?</c>
<c.yellow>No, it's work.</c>

00:17:42.960 --> 00:17:44.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I've been invited to a symposium</c>

00:17:44.960 --> 00:17:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>on violent offenders</c>
<c.yellow>with repeat pattern disorder.</c>

00:17:47.960 --> 00:17:49.960 align:middle line:-3
Hmm, she's going
to a serial killers' convention.

00:17:49.960 --> 00:17:51.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>That's very reductive of you,</c>
<c.yellow>Martin.</c>

00:17:51.960 --> 00:17:54.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Though not entirely inaccurate.</c>

00:17:54.960 --> 00:17:57.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Hello, James Henry.</c>

00:17:57.480 --> 00:17:58.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Nice briefcase.</c>

00:17:58.960 --> 00:18:00.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Thank you.</c>

00:18:02.160 --> 00:18:04.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Martin. Could I have a quiet word?</c>

00:18:04.960 --> 00:18:06.960 align:middle line:-2
Yes. Yes, of course.

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.640 align:middle line:-2
Yeah. Er, go through.

00:18:10.960 --> 00:18:12.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Oh, it looks different.</c>
Hmm. It is.

00:18:12.960 --> 00:18:14.960 align:middle line:-2
Louisa's using it.

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>And you're happy with that?</c>
Yes, course I am.

00:18:17.960 --> 00:18:20.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Then why are we doing</c>
<c.yellow>so much work on your blood phobia?</c>

00:18:20.960 --> 00:18:22.960 align:middle line:-2
How are they connected?

00:18:22.960 --> 00:18:25.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Well, I presumed that the plan was</c>

00:18:25.960 --> 00:18:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>that we rectified your mistake</c>
<c.yellow>and you became a doctor again.</c>

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:31.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>But now that you've given up</c>
<c.yellow>your consulting room...</c>

00:18:31.800 --> 00:18:32.960 align:middle line:-2
Well, you can presume all you want.

00:18:32.960 --> 00:18:35.960 align:middle line:-3
I never said that I was planning
a return to medicine.

00:18:35.960 --> 00:18:36.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>But it's what you want.</c>

00:18:36.960 --> 00:18:39.960 align:middle line:-3
I haven't considered all my options.
I've been too busy with Mary.

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:42.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You've written a paper</c>
<c.yellow>for The Lancet,</c>

00:18:42.960 --> 00:18:45.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>you're doing extracurricular</c>
<c.yellow>medical research,</c>

00:18:45.960 --> 00:18:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>you're working</c>
<c.yellow>on your blood phobia,</c>

00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:49.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>you even invented the Ellingham Cup.</c>

00:18:49.960 --> 00:18:51.960 align:middle line:-2
Well, invented is a strong word.

00:18:51.960 --> 00:18:55.800 align:middle line:-3
I just modified, and slightly
improved the existing ventouse.

00:18:55.800 --> 00:18:58.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Exactly. For someone who isn't</c>
<c.yellow>planning to go back to medicine,</c>

00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:01.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>you seem keenly involved</c>
<c.yellow>in it still.</c>

00:19:01.640 --> 00:19:04.160 align:middle line:-3
Er, it's...
It's an area of interest.

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:07.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>You're waiting, aren't you?</c>

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:10.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You're waiting for them</c>
<c.yellow>to ask you back.</c>

00:19:10.960 --> 00:19:12.960 align:middle line:-2
No. Of course I'm not.

00:19:12.960 --> 00:19:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You know it doesn't work like that.</c>
<c.yellow>You know you have to reach out.</c>

00:19:15.960 --> 00:19:18.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You have to reach out</c>
<c.yellow>to someone like Chris Parsons.</c>

00:19:18.800 --> 00:19:21.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>And you haven't, have you?</c>
No, I haven't.

00:19:21.960 --> 00:19:23.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Are you afraid?</c>
Oh, now you're being ridiculous.

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:25.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Well, if you reach out</c>
<c.yellow>and you're rejected,</c>

00:19:25.960 --> 00:19:27.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>that's it, it's over,</c>
<c.yellow>there's no going back.</c>

00:19:27.960 --> 00:19:29.960 align:middle line:-3
You realise this is
all in your mind, don't you?

00:19:29.960 --> 00:19:31.480 align:middle line:-2
I haven't said a word of this.

00:19:31.480 --> 00:19:34.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Well, that's what concerns me,</c>
<c.yellow>Martin.</c>

00:19:34.960 --> 00:19:36.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>So much unsaid.</c>

00:19:36.960 --> 00:19:40.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>So many things that you won't admit.</c>

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:44.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Until you do,</c>
<c.yellow>things won't get any better.</c>

00:19:44.960 --> 00:19:50.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>All that training,</c>
<c.yellow>all those years of practice...</c>

00:19:50.480 --> 00:19:55.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>to end up mending</c>
