Just here on the left.
<c.yellow>Oh, right.</c>

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:39.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It's got a certain rustic charm.</c>

00:20:39.960 --> 00:20:41.960 align:middle line:-3
No-one's gonna want
to rent this dump!

00:20:41.960 --> 00:20:43.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>No, come on.</c>

00:20:43.960 --> 00:20:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I mean, all it needs is</c>
<c.yellow>a bit of spit and... and polish.</c>

00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:50.480 align:middle line:-2
I'm gonna be a trainee forever!

00:20:52.960 --> 00:20:54.960 align:middle line:-2
FLIES BUZZ

00:21:01.960 --> 00:21:04.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>What's that?</c>

