for nearly 45 miles.

00:21:11.960 --> 00:21:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>A little gory for a four-year-old.</c>
DOORBELL RINGS

00:21:15.960 --> 00:21:18.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Maybe you could both read the book</c>
<c.cyan>about the talking sausage instead.</c>

00:21:21.960 --> 00:21:24.000 align:middle line:-3
And we call the study of all this
neurology.

00:21:24.000 --> 00:21:25.960 align:middle line:-3
Can you say that?
<c.green>Neurology.</c>

00:21:25.960 --> 00:21:27.480 align:middle line:-2
Yes. Very good.

00:21:28.960 --> 00:21:29.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Dylan.</c>

00:21:30.960 --> 00:21:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Is everything OK?</c>
<c.green>Yeah.</c>

00:21:36.960 --> 00:21:40.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Mum's being weird again.</c>
<c.green>I didn't know where else to go.</c>

00:21:40.960 --> 00:21:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, why don't I walk you home</c>
<c.cyan>and we'll see how she is?</c>

00:21:43.960 --> 00:21:44.960 align:middle line:-2
Maybe I should come with you.

00:21:44.960 --> 00:21:46.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>My mum doesn't like you.</c>

