00:21:47.960 --> 00:21:50.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, someone needs to stay home</c>
<c.cyan>and look after the children.</c>

00:21:50.960 --> 00:21:52.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>So I'll call you</c>
<c.cyan>if there are any problems.</c>

00:21:58.160 --> 00:22:02.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Oh. I'm fine,</c>
<c.yellow>it's a fuss about nothing.</c>

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:04.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>You fell asleep</c>
<c.green>on the kitchen floor.</c>

00:22:04.960 --> 00:22:06.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>No, look, I just...</c>

00:22:06.960 --> 00:22:12.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Mummy was tired and I just decided</c>
<c.yellow>to close my eyes for a minute.</c>

00:22:12.960 --> 00:22:14.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>And snore.</c>

00:22:14.960 --> 00:22:16.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Yeah. That is a little strange.</c>

00:22:16.960 --> 00:22:18.800 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Oh, look, I'm not disagreeing.</c>

00:22:18.800 --> 00:22:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I've just been under a lot of strain</c>
<c.yellow>recently with the custody battle.</c>

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:24.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Yeah, you do seem quite rundown.</c>

00:22:26.640 --> 00:22:27.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It's a marathon.</c>

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:30.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>But the finish line is in sight.</c>

00:22:30.320 --> 00:22:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I've got a court hearing</c>
<c.yellow>in the morning, so...</c>

00:22:33.960 --> 00:22:35.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>fingers crossed.</c>

00:22:36.960 --> 00:22:39.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Came as fast as I could. </c>Thank you.
You know where everything is.

00:22:39.960 --> 00:22:41.960 align:middle line:-3
There's a sandwich for James here
and I won't be long.

00:22:41.960 --> 00:22:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Are you gonna pay me extra?</c>
What for?

00:22:43.960 --> 00:22:46.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I had to close my salon</c>
<c.green>to come here, you know.</c>

00:22:46.160 --> 00:22:48.960 align:middle line:-3
Did you have any customers?
<c.green>That's not the point.</c>

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:50.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>You're treating me</c>
<c.green>like a haddock nanny.</c>

