I'll pay you what I paid you before.
Thank you.

00:23:03.960 --> 00:23:05.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Look, I know Martin</c>
<c.cyan>isn't registered,</c>

00:23:05.960 --> 00:23:06.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>but when it comes</c>
<c.cyan>to medical issues...</c>

00:23:06.960 --> 00:23:08.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>you know, he was a doctor.</c>

00:23:08.160 --> 00:23:09.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Well, he IS a doctor.</c>

00:23:09.960 --> 00:23:11.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>He really does know</c>
<c.cyan>what he's talking about.</c>

00:23:11.960 --> 00:23:13.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Oh, I don't know...</c>

00:23:13.960 --> 00:23:15.800 align:middle line:-3
