<c.yellow>been going,</c>

00:23:15.800 --> 00:23:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I don't want to give my ex</c>
<c.yellow>any more ammunition.</c>

00:23:17.960 --> 00:23:20.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Anything you discuss with him</c>
<c.cyan>would be completely confidential.</c>

00:23:22.960 --> 00:23:24.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>And I know it doesn't seem like it,</c>

00:23:24.480 --> 00:23:26.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>but, you know,</c>
<c.cyan>he does just wanna help.</c>

00:23:26.160 --> 00:23:27.960 align:middle line:-2
KNOCKING AT DOOR

00:23:29.160 --> 00:23:32.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Oh, great. That's all I need.</c>
<c.yellow>Let me get rid of them.</c>

00:23:37.320 --> 00:23:38.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Yeah...</c>
SIGHS

00:23:38.960 --> 00:23:41.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>What do you want?</c>
I'd like to examine you.

00:23:43.160 --> 00:23:46.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Look... you can't just show up</c>
<c.yellow>on people's doorsteps</c>

00:23:46.160 --> 00:23:47.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>and start harassing them.</c>

00:23:47.960 --> 00:23:49.960 align:middle line:-3
You have ptosis.
Your eyelids are drooping.

00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:52.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>What...?! You're not a doctor!</c>

00:23:52.960 --> 00:23:54.960 align:middle line:-3
That's a technicality.
<c.yellow>No, it's not.</c>

00:23:54.960 --> 00:23:56.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>For all I know,</c>
<c.yellow>you might have been struck off</c>

00:23:56.960 --> 00:23:58.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>for being a big bloody weirdo.</c>

00:23:58.960 --> 00:24:01.960 align:middle line:-3
I resigned.
This isn't about me.

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:03.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Martin, what are you doing here?</c>

00:24:03.960 --> 00:24:06.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>And who's looking after</c>
<c.cyan>the children? </c>Janice.

00:24:06.960 --> 00:24:09.960 align:middle line:-3
I'm concerned that you are suffering
from myasthenia gravis.

00:24:09.960 --> 00:24:13.160 align:middle line:-3
Which is a neuromuscular condition
that causes muscle weakness.

00:24:13.160 --> 00:24:14.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I thought you said it was ptosis?</c>

00:24:14.960 --> 00:24:17.160 align:middle line:-3
One doesn't preclude the other.
<c.yellow>That's convenient (!)</c>

00:24:17.160 --> 00:24:20.960 align:middle line:-3
You need to seek medical help.
<c.yellow>I have.</c>

00:24:20.960 --> 00:24:22.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>OK, look, I visited a naturopath</c>

00:24:22.960 --> 00:24:25.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>and I'm being tested</c>
<c.yellow>for food allergies.</c>

00:24:25.320 --> 00:24:26.960 align:middle line:-2
That's not a doctor.

00:24:26.960 --> 00:24:29.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Just leave.</c>
<c.cyan>I told you I would handle this.</c>

00:24:29.960 --> 00:24:32.160 align:middle line:-3
Louisa, with respect,
she doesn't need a child counsellor,

00:24:32.160 --> 00:24:34.320 align:middle line:-3
she doesn't need
to see a naturopath,

00:24:34.320 --> 00:24:36.960 align:middle line:-3
or a wizard,
she needs to see a doctor.

00:24:36.960 --> 00:24:42.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>"She" is suffering from stress</c>
<c.yellow>and has a lot going on in her life.</c>

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:44.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>But OK, fine, fine,</c>

00:24:44.960 --> 00:24:49.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>when I have more time,</c>
<c.yellow>I will go and see a REAL DOCTOR.</c>

00:24:49.320 --> 00:24:50.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>OK?</c>

00:24:50.960 --> 00:24:55.800 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>But YOU have five seconds!</c>

00:24:55.800 --> 00:24:56.960 align:middle line:-2
To examine you?

00:24:56.960 --> 00:24:59.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>To leave me alone</c>
<c.yellow>or I'm calling the police.</c>

00:25:01.960 --> 00:25:03.960 align:middle line:-2
I am a doctor!

00:25:05.960 --> 00:25:08.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>And then you proceeded</c>
<c.green>to tell the complainant</c>

00:25:08.640 --> 00:25:10.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>that she was "stubborn and..."</c>

00:25:12.960 --> 00:25:16.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Can't read my own writing there.</c>
<c.green>Is that an idiot or imbecile?</c>

00:25:16.960 --> 00:25:19.160 align:middle line:-3
Both are applicable.
<c.green>That's not very nice.</c>

