Neither is respiratory failure
with oropharyngeal collapse

00:25:22.960 --> 00:25:24.960 align:middle line:-2
caused by a myasthenic crisis.

00:25:24.960 --> 00:25:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Is that a threat?</c>
What? No. It's a concern.

00:25:28.960 --> 00:25:32.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Look...</c>
<c.green>You're not the doc any more, Doc.</c>

00:25:32.960 --> 00:25:35.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>You can't just go barging</c>
<c.green>into people's houses</c>

00:25:35.320 --> 00:25:36.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>and start barking at them.</c>

00:25:36.960 --> 00:25:42.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Consider this an informal caution.</c>
<c.green>You stay away from her.</c>

00:25:42.800 --> 00:25:43.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Laying down the law there, Joe.</c>

00:25:43.960 --> 00:25:46.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Just doing my job.</c>

00:25:46.320 --> 00:25:48.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>I'll see myself out.</c>

00:25:52.960 --> 00:25:54.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Thanks for looking after</c>
<c.cyan>James and Mary, Janice.</c>

00:25:54.960 --> 00:25:57.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>If you need anything,</c>
<c.yellow>just let me know,</c>

00:25:57.640 --> 00:25:58.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I am always available.</c>

00:25:58.960 --> 00:26:00.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Not that I'm desperate or anything.</c>

00:26:00.960 --> 00:26:03.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>It's not like I spent</c>
<c.yellow>all my life savings on a nail salon</c>

00:26:03.960 --> 00:26:06.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>that no-one visits, and I'm</c>
<c.yellow>facing crippling debt and ruin.</c>

00:26:06.960 --> 00:26:08.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Thank you.</c>
<c.cyan>Thanks.</c>

00:26:15.960 --> 00:26:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>What on earth were you doing,</c>
<c.cyan>showing up like that?</c>

00:26:17.960 --> 00:26:20.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>You've jeopardised</c>
<c.cyan>my job and reputation.</c>

00:26:20.480 --> 00:26:21.960 align:middle line:-2
That woman needs help.

00:26:21.960 --> 00:26:23.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Yes. And I was making progress</c>
<c.cyan>with her, Martin.</c>

00:26:25.960 --> 00:26:29.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>You know, I've been patient,</c>
<c.cyan>and I've given it time...</c>

00:26:31.960 --> 00:26:33.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>..but we can't go on like this.</c>

00:26:33.960 --> 00:26:36.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>YOU can't go on like this.</c>

00:26:36.480 --> 00:26:37.960 align:middle line:-2
She is ill.

00:26:37.960 --> 00:26:39.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Do you regret resigning?</c>

00:26:42.960 --> 00:26:44.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Do you wish you were still a doctor?</c>

00:26:47.960 --> 00:26:51.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>It's been a year, Martin. Please.</c>
<c.cyan>Just... just say something.</c>

00:26:54.000 --> 00:26:55.960 align:middle line:-2
Yes.

00:26:55.960 --> 00:26:58.000 align:middle line:-2
I made a mistake.

00:26:58.000 --> 00:26:59.960 align:middle line:-2
I thought, erm...

00:26:59.960 --> 00:27:02.960 align:middle line:-3
I thought that
they'd realise that and, er...

00:27:02.960 --> 00:27:05.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>And everything</c>
<c.cyan>would just go back to normal?</c>

00:27:05.960 --> 00:27:08.960 align:middle line:-3
I didn't think
it would go on this long.

00:27:08.960 --> 00:27:10.960 align:middle line:-2
And now, I don't know what to do.

00:27:10.960 --> 00:27:12.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>You need to contact them.</c>

00:27:15.480 --> 00:27:16.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>And you need to apologise.</c>

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:19.960 align:middle line:-3
I haven't done anything
to apologise for.

00:27:19.960 --> 00:27:21.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Look, I can speak to Abigail,</c>

00:27:21.160 --> 00:27:24.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>and convince her to see a doctor</c>
<c.cyan>sooner if it's urgent. </c>It is.

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:26.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>But it's not just her.</c>

00:27:26.960 --> 00:27:29.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>What about the next person,</c>
<c.cyan>and the person after that?</c>

00:27:29.960 --> 00:27:32.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>And all those people</c>
<c.cyan>you won't be able to help?</c>

00:27:35.800 --> 00:27:38.960 align:middle line:-2
You're right. I'll call Chris.

00:28:00.960 --> 00:28:02.800 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Martin. What are you doing here?</c>

00:28:02.800 --> 00:28:05.640 align:middle line:-3
