Heidi said you were playing golf.

00:28:05.640 --> 00:28:07.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Helen. Is everything all right?</c>
I need your help.

00:28:07.960 --> 00:28:10.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Why, have you decided you want</c>
<c.yellow>to become a doctor again?</c>

00:28:10.960 --> 00:28:12.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Oh, Martin. It was a joke. Martin.</c>

00:28:15.960 --> 00:28:16.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Oh, no, no, no...</c>

00:28:16.960 --> 00:28:17.960 align:middle line:-2
What steps do I have to take

00:28:17.960 --> 00:28:19.960 align:middle line:-3
to get registered again
as soon as possible?

00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>After what happened last time?</c>
<c.yellow>Goodbye, Martin.</c>

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:24.960 align:middle line:-3
There's a patient
that needs my help.

00:28:24.960 --> 00:28:25.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Yeah. Then tell 'em to see a doctor.</c>

00:28:25.960 --> 00:28:27.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, by the time she does,
it might be too late.

00:28:27.960 --> 00:28:30.480 align:middle line:-3
She won't let me examine her
because I'm not registered.

00:28:30.480 --> 00:28:32.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Do you hate me, Martin?</c>
No, of course I don't.

00:28:32.800 --> 00:28:33.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It feels like you hate me.</c>

00:28:33.960 --> 00:28:36.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Or maybe you derive</c>
<c.yellow>a subconscious element of pleasure</c>

00:28:36.000 --> 00:28:37.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>from torturing me.</c>

00:28:37.960 --> 00:28:38.960 align:middle line:-2
That's a bit overdramatic.

00:28:38.960 --> 00:28:39.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>And with very good reason.</c>

00:28:39.960 --> 00:28:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I stood there</c>
<c.yellow>and defended you to the GMC,</c>

00:28:43.960 --> 00:28:47.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>and all the while you'd already</c>
<c.yellow>sent them your resignation!</c>

00:28:47.480 --> 00:28:48.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I looked like a complete idiot.</c>

00:28:48.960 --> 00:28:53.160 align:middle line:-3
Yeah, I meant to tell you.
