00:28:53.160 --> 00:28:54.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Never again, Martin.</c>

00:28:57.800 --> 00:28:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Even if I could help you,</c>
<c.yellow>it's not up to me.</c>

00:28:59.960 --> 00:29:02.160 align:middle line:-3
Whose decision is it?
<c.yellow>Professor Langan's.</c>

00:29:02.160 --> 00:29:04.960 align:middle line:-3
Can you get me a meeting
with Langan?

00:29:04.960 --> 00:29:08.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>He chaired your hearing panel.</c>
<c.yellow>You threw up in his bin.</c>

00:29:08.960 --> 00:29:10.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I won't ask him again.</c>

00:29:13.000 --> 00:29:15.160 align:middle line:-3
I've worked on the blood phobia
with my aunt.

00:29:15.160 --> 00:29:18.960 align:middle line:-3
And I happen to know that
the NHS is desperate for rural GPs.

00:29:18.960 --> 00:29:24.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>But you haven't changed,</c>
<c.yellow>Martin, and that's what they wanted.</c>

00:29:24.000 --> 00:29:25.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>I mean, look at you.</c>

00:29:25.960 --> 00:29:27.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You show up here,</c>
<c.yellow>start making demands</c>

00:29:27.960 --> 00:29:30.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>without so much as a,</c>
<c.yellow>"Hello," or, "How are you?"</c>

00:29:30.960 --> 00:29:32.960 align:middle line:-3
How are you?
<c.yellow>I'm fine.</c>

00:29:33.960 --> 00:29:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Helen and I are giving</c>
<c.yellow>the marriage another go.</c>

00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:38.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Work's been quite stressful.</c>

00:29:38.960 --> 00:29:42.160 align:middle line:-3
Oh, I'm sorry to hear that,
er, but I'm glad that you and...

00:29:42.160 --> 00:29:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Helen.</c>
..Helen are working things out.

00:29:43.960 --> 00:29:45.960 align:middle line:-2
And if I'm brusque, it's because

00:29:45.960 --> 00:29:48.960 align:middle line:-3
I realise that I made
a mistake in resigning.

00:29:48.960 --> 00:29:51.960 align:middle line:-3
And I'm not used
to asking for help.

00:29:54.960 --> 00:29:57.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I don't think I've ever heard you</c>
<c.yellow>admit to making a mistake before.</c>

00:29:59.800 --> 00:30:01.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It's quite strange.</c>

00:30:01.160 --> 00:30:03.640 align:middle line:-3
Why don't I just go and see
Langan right now?

00:30:03.640 --> 00:30:04.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>God, no, you can't just show up!</c>

00:30:04.960 --> 00:30:07.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I need to...</c>
<c.yellow>have a word with him first.</c>

00:30:07.960 --> 00:30:09.480 align:middle line:-2
When?

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:11.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>We've got a budget meeting at the</c>
<c.yellow>PCT headquarters tomorrow morning,</c>

00:30:11.960 --> 00:30:13.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>9:00 till 10:30.</c>

00:30:13.000 --> 00:30:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'll prep him,</c>
<c.yellow>and then you can plead your case.</c>

00:30:15.960 --> 00:30:20.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You'll get one shot at this,</c>
<c.yellow>Martin, so be prepared.</c>

00:30:20.960 --> 00:30:24.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You're gonna have to grovel</c>
<c.yellow>like you've never grovelled before.</c>

00:30:25.960 --> 00:30:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>And even then,</c>
<c.yellow>he will probably say no.</c>

00:30:30.640 --> 00:30:32.960 align:middle line:-3
In the meantime, is it all right
to examine this patient?

00:30:32.960 --> 00:30:34.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Absolutely not!</c>

00:30:34.320 --> 00:30:37.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You're not a doctor yet,</c>
<c.yellow>so don't go jeopardising things.</c>

00:30:39.000 --> 00:30:41.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It's all very delicate.</c>

00:30:41.960 --> 00:30:45.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You can recommend her to someone.</c>
<c.yellow>That's all.</c>

00:30:45.960 --> 00:30:48.960 align:middle line:-2
I understand. 10:30.

00:30:59.960 --> 00:31:01.960 align:middle line:-2
Mrs Tishell. What do you want?

00:31:01.960 --> 00:31:05.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I just wanted you to check my hand,</c>
<c.cyan>to see if it's healing properly.</c>

00:31:05.960 --> 00:31:06.960 align:middle line:-2
Right. Come through.

00:31:11.960 --> 00:31:13.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Oh, Doctor!</c>

00:31:13.960 --> 00:31:16.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>What has she done</c>
<c.cyan>to your lovely room?</c>

00:31:16.960 --> 00:31:18.800 align:middle line:-2
Here. I'll look at it here.

00:31:22.320 --> 00:31:23.960 align:middle line:-2
Yes, that's healing well.

00:31:25.960 --> 00:31:27.320 align:middle line:-2
Why are there three staple wounds?

00:31:27.320 --> 00:31:31.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, erm, I was just putting up</c>
<c.cyan>a poster advertising a sale,</c>

00:31:31.960 --> 00:31:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>and stupidly I put my hand</c>
<c.cyan>in the wrong place.</c>

00:31:33.960 --> 00:31:36.960 align:middle line:-3
Yeah, one I can understand,
maybe two. But three?

00:31:38.960 --> 00:31:40.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>One wasn't enough.</c>

00:31:40.960 --> 00:31:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I thought if there was</c>
<c.cyan>a medical situation, then...</c>

00:31:43.960 --> 00:31:46.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>maybe you'd remember</c>
<c.cyan>how it felt to be a doctor</c>

00:31:46.960 --> 00:31:48.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>and then you'd come back.</c>

00:31:48.960 --> 00:31:51.960 align:middle line:-3
That's idiotic.
<c.cyan>Is it?</c>

00:31:51.960 --> 00:31:55.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Is it idiotic to stand up</c>
<c.cyan>for something you believe in?</c>

00:31:55.960 --> 00:32:00.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>To be a lone voice,</c>
<c.cyan>shouting above an indifferent tide?</c>

00:32:00.960 --> 00:32:06.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>To try to breathe life back into</c>
<c.cyan>the weary soul of a once great man?</c>

00:32:06.640 --> 00:32:11.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>If that is idiotic,</c>
<c.cyan>then I am guilty as charged.</c>

00:32:11.960 --> 00:32:14.960 align:middle line:-3
Yeah, stapling your hand
on purpose is idiotic.

00:32:14.960 --> 00:32:17.960 align:middle line:-3
You shouldn't do it again.
Thank you, Mrs Tishell.

00:32:21.960 --> 00:32:24.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Hi, Sally. How's your hand?</c>
<c.cyan>It was an accident.</c>

00:32:25.960 --> 00:32:29.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>So, well, how did it go with Chris?</c>
<c.yellow>Can he get you your job back?</c>

00:32:29.640 --> 00:32:32.160 align:middle line:-3
He's going to have a try. I'm going
to the PCT office in Exeter

00:32:32.160 --> 00:32:34.960 align:middle line:-3
at 10:30 tomorrow morning, to have
a meeting with Professor Langan.

00:32:34.960 --> 00:32:37.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Oh, that sounds promising.</c>

00:32:43.960 --> 00:32:46.960 align:middle line:-2
DISTANT SNORING

00:32:49.960 --> 00:32:51.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Al.</c>

00:32:52.640 --> 00:32:54.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Al!</c>

00:32:57.960 --> 00:33:01.480 align:middle line:-3
What?
<c.cyan>It's been hours.</c>

00:33:01.480 --> 00:33:02.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>You have to do something.</c>

00:33:02.960 --> 00:33:05.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, I can't just kick him out
on the street, can I?

00:33:05.960 --> 00:33:07.960 align:middle line:-3
I need to find something
like the pub, where...

00:33:07.960 --> 00:33:10.800 align:middle line:-2
where he can live and work...

00:33:10.800 --> 00:33:11.960 align:middle line:-2
HE YAWNS

00:33:11.960 --> 00:33:14.640 align:middle line:-2
But can I do it in the morning?

00:33:17.160 --> 00:33:19.960 align:middle line:-3
SNORING CONTINUES,
SHE GROANS

00:33:26.960 --> 00:33:29.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Now, remember,</c>
<c.cyan>not to run in the corridors.</c>

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:31.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>And listen to the teachers.</c>

00:33:31.960 --> 00:33:34.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Can you take her?</c>
<c.cyan>Have you got her? </c>Mm-hm.

00:33:37.000 --> 00:33:41.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>And if anyone makes fun</c>
<c.cyan>of your briefcase, you just laugh.</c>

00:33:41.960 --> 00:33:42.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE LAUGHS

00:33:42.960 --> 00:33:44.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>You laugh</c>
<c.cyan>like you're in on the joke.</c>

00:33:44.960 --> 00:33:46.320 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Stop fussing, Mum.</c>

00:33:46.320 --> 00:33:48.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>It's your first day at school,</c>
<c.cyan>I'm allowed to fuss.</c>

00:33:48.800 --> 00:33:50.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Will you have time to come with us?</c>
Er, yes.

00:33:50.960 --> 00:33:52.960 align:middle line:-3
As long as I leave by 8:30,
I should make it.

00:33:52.960 --> 00:33:57.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Now, before you say anything,</c>
<c.yellow>erm, it is a fixer-upper. </c>Yeah.

00:33:57.960 --> 00:34:00.960 align:middle line:-3
Don't see it for what it is,
see it for what it could be.

00:34:00.960 --> 00:34:04.640 align:middle line:-3
A bustling caravan park,
full of life and colour.

00:34:04.640 --> 00:34:06.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>So I would live on-site, right?</c>
That's the idea.

00:34:06.960 --> 00:34:08.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, I've always liked</c>
<c.cyan>a mobile home.</c>

00:34:08.960 --> 00:34:09.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Perhaps I could change the name?</c>

00:34:09.960 --> 00:34:12.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Large Caravan Park...?</c>
<c.yellow>Well, no.</c>

00:34:12.960 --> 00:34:16.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>No, because that just makes it sound</c>
<c.yellow>like a really big caravan park.</c>

00:34:16.800 --> 00:34:18.960 align:middle line:-3
You could do what you like, Bert.
You'd be the boss.

00:34:20.960 --> 00:34:22.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>I'll take it.</c>

00:34:22.160 --> 00:34:24.640 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>You're smart to move fast, Mr Large.</c>

00:34:24.640 --> 00:34:27.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Very popular location,</c>
<c.green>lots of enquiries about it.</c>

00:34:27.960 --> 00:34:29.960 align:middle line:-2
Oh, and here is the paperwork.

00:34:29.960 --> 00:34:32.000 align:middle line:-3
And we would need
two months' rent upfront.

00:34:32.000 --> 00:34:35.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Oh, I-I do have</c>
<c.cyan>a slight cash flow problem.</c>

00:34:35.960 --> 00:34:39.960 align:middle line:-3
OK, erm, well, I'm sure we could
arrange a structured payment plan.

00:34:39.960 --> 00:34:40.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Within reason.</c>

00:34:40.960 --> 00:34:42.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Well, here's what I'm thinking,</c>
<c.cyan>right?</c>

00:34:42.960 --> 00:34:45.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I get the park, and maybe</c>
<c.cyan>an advance for renovations.</c>

00:34:45.960 --> 00:34:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>And then I repay it</c>
<c.cyan>once I've made the money back.</c>

00:34:47.960 --> 00:34:49.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE LAUGHS

00:34:49.960 --> 00:34:54.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Sorry.</c>
<c.green>You want us to give you money?</c>

00:34:54.960 --> 00:34:56.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I don't have any.</c>
<c.yellow>But, but what about your nest egg?</c>

00:34:56.960 --> 00:34:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I didn't want you to feel sorry</c>
<c.cyan>for me.</c>

00:34:59.960 --> 00:35:02.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>It's embarrassing to get to my age</c>
<c.cyan>and have nothing to show for it.</c>

00:35:02.000 --> 00:35:05.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I knew it was a mistake giving</c>
<c.green>this property to a trainee.</c>

00:35:05.320 --> 00:35:06.960 align:middle line:-3
No, wait.. Wait, wait, wait.
Just wait.

00:35:08.960 --> 00:35:10.960 align:middle line:-2
Al...

00:35:10.960 --> 00:35:13.960 align:middle line:-3
Didn't you tell me yesterday, you're
about to spend a load of money

00:35:13.960 --> 00:35:15.960 align:middle line:-3
to store your
food trucks and supplies?

00:35:15.960 --> 00:35:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Yeah.</c>
So what if you took that money

00:35:17.960 --> 00:35:21.960 align:middle line:-3
and used it to cover the monthly
rent for this place instead?

00:35:21.960 --> 00:35:23.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>What about the trucks and supplies?</c>
Well, look around.

00:35:23.960 --> 00:35:26.960 align:middle line:-3
You could store them here.
It's a win-win.

00:35:26.960 --> 00:35:30.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Now, that sounds a lot like I'm</c>
<c.yellow>going into business with Dad, and...</c>

00:35:30.640 --> 00:35:32.960 align:middle line:-2
Have you got any better ideas?

00:35:32.960 --> 00:35:35.960 align:middle line:-3
I mean, I know you love having
your dad staying with us...

00:35:37.800 --> 00:35:39.480 align:middle line:-2
HE SIGHS

00:35:39.480 --> 00:35:41.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Hey, Dad?</c>
<c.cyan>Yeah?</c>

00:35:41.960 --> 00:35:44.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Erm, pick a caravan.</c>
<c.cyan>Why?</c>

00:35:44.960 --> 00:35:45.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Well, cos I wanna know</c>

00:35:45.960 --> 00:35:49.480 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>which one you're gonna choose</c>
<c.yellow>as your new home.</c>

00:35:49.480 --> 00:35:51.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>What about that one, then?</c>
<c.yellow>Er...</c>

00:35:51.000 --> 00:35:53.960 align:middle line:-3
Not that one.
We'll get the cleaners in first.

00:35:55.960 --> 00:35:57.800 align:middle line:-2
Thank you.

00:35:59.800 --> 00:36:03.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Am I, erm, hearing right?</c>
Yeah. All signed and sealed.

00:36:07.000 --> 00:36:09.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Congratulations, young lady.</c>

00:36:09.480 --> 00:36:11.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Welcome to the big league.</c>

00:36:11.960 --> 00:36:15.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I told you, boy. You and me.</c>
<c.cyan>It's like fate.</c>

00:36:26.800 --> 00:36:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>It's a big day, their first day.</c>
<c.cyan>Oh.</c>

00:36:28.960 --> 00:36:31.000 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>You think I'd be used to it,</c>

00:36:31.000 --> 00:36:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>but it's so weird being on</c>
<c.cyan>the other side, and saying goodbye.</c>

00:36:33.960 --> 00:36:36.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Goodbye!</c>
<c.cyan>No, I didn't mean...!</c>

00:36:37.640 --> 00:36:38.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>There we go.</c>

00:36:38.960 --> 00:36:42.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Must be emotional for you, too.</c>

00:36:42.960 --> 00:36:46.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>And how are you doing? It's a big</c>
<c.cyan>day for you, too, isn't it?</c>

00:36:46.160 --> 00:36:48.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Officially the head,</c>
<c.green>no longer acting.</c>

00:36:48.960 --> 00:36:53.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>The crown is mine and they'll have</c>
<c.green>to pry it from my cold, dead hands.</c>

00:36:55.480 --> 00:36:58.960 align:middle line:-2
Wait a moment!

00:36:58.960 --> 00:37:00.960 align:middle line:-2
Don't drive this car.

00:37:00.960 --> 00:37:02.960 align:middle line:-3
Don't drive the car!
TYRES SQUEAL

00:37:08.960 --> 00:37:10.960 align:middle line:-2
Follow that car.

00:37:10.960 --> 00:37:14.960 align:middle line:-3
It's that woman.
The, erm, the sick one.

00:37:14.960 --> 00:37:16.960 align:middle line:-3
The one you told me to stay away
from. <c.yellow>Abigail Gillman?</c>

00:37:16.960 --> 00:37:19.960 align:middle line:-3
Yeah. <c.yellow>Doc, you can't keep</c>
<c.yellow>harassing that woman.</c>

00:37:19.960 --> 00:37:21.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'm gonna have to issue you</c>
<c.yellow>a formal warning.</c>

00:37:21.960 --> 00:37:23.960 align:middle line:-3
She's not fit to drive,
she can barely walk.

00:37:23.960 --> 00:37:26.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>A traffic violation?</c>
<c.yellow>Why didn't you say so?</c>

00:37:26.960 --> 00:37:28.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Hold on to your hat.</c>

00:37:43.960 --> 00:37:46.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'm not actually allowed to</c>
<c.yellow>issue you with a formal warning,</c>

00:37:46.960 --> 00:37:48.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>it's above my rank.</c>

00:37:49.960 --> 00:37:51.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Exciting saying it, though.</c>

00:37:57.960 --> 00:37:59.960 align:middle line:-3
There she is.
<c.yellow>Right. Here we go.</c>

00:37:59.960 --> 00:38:01.800 align:middle line:-2
SIREN BLARES

00:38:04.960 --> 00:38:06.960 align:middle line:-2
SHE SIGHS

00:38:15.160 --> 00:38:17.960 align:middle line:-2
TYRES SQUEAL

00:38:21.480 --> 00:38:23.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>That's not good.</c>
Call an ambulance.

00:38:31.480 --> 00:38:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'll get a first-aid kit.</c>
<c.yellow>Ambulance, please.</c>

00:38:33.960 --> 00:38:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>There's been a road traffic</c>
<c.yellow>incident, Portwenn A road...</c>

00:38:39.960 --> 00:38:42.000 align:middle line:-2
CREAKING

00:39:14.480 --> 00:39:15.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Doc?</c>

00:39:15.960 --> 00:39:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Don't panic.</c>
I'm not.

00:39:17.960 --> 00:39:21.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>OK, well, panic a bit because</c>
<c.yellow>the car's about to go over a cliff.</c>

00:39:21.160 --> 00:39:23.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>You need to get out.</c>
No, I can't. I have to do this.

00:39:23.960 --> 00:39:25.640 align:middle line:-3
Steady the car.
<c.yellow>Right.</c>

00:39:25.640 --> 00:39:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I've got a winch in the jeep.</c>
No, stay here and steady...!

00:39:38.960 --> 00:39:40.960 align:middle line:-3
I'm going
to insert an endotracheal tube

00:39:40.960 --> 00:39:42.960 align:middle line:-3
through your nose
to help you breathe.

00:39:52.960 --> 00:39:54.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Is she breathing?</c>
No, that's why I'm ventilating her.

00:39:54.960 --> 00:39:56.960 align:middle line:-2
Did you get the winch?

00:39:56.960 --> 00:39:59.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>So, it turns out</c>
<c.yellow>I don't actually have a winch.</c>

00:40:06.960 --> 00:40:09.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Doc, you need to get out of here.</c>

00:40:09.960 --> 00:40:13.000 align:middle line:-3
It's too dangerous to move.
<c.yellow>It's too dangerous not to move.</c>

00:40:13.000 --> 00:40:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>If I pull her out</c>
<c.yellow>at the same time,</c>

00:40:15.960 --> 00:40:18.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>the counterweight</c>
<c.yellow>will balance the things.</c>

00:40:18.320 --> 00:40:20.160 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>It's basic chemistry.</c>

00:40:20.160 --> 00:40:22.960 align:middle line:-3
Physics.
<c.yellow>Exactly!</c>

00:40:22.960 --> 00:40:26.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Ma'am, I'm gonna have to be</c>
<c.yellow>a little bit rough.</c>

00:40:26.960 --> 00:40:28.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>For that, I apologise.</c>

00:40:28.960 --> 00:40:31.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>All right, Doc.</c>
<c.yellow>On the count of ten. </c>Ten?!

00:40:31.960 --> 00:40:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Right, no, five would be better.</c>
<c.yellow>It's much quicker.</c>

00:40:33.960 --> 00:40:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Actually, now I think about it,</c>
<c.yellow>we could just do it in...</c>

00:40:36.960 --> 00:40:38.960 align:middle line:-3
Just do it now! Ready?
<c.yellow>OK. </c>GO!

00:40:39.960 --> 00:40:41.960 align:middle line:-2
OK.

00:40:41.960 --> 00:40:44.960 align:middle line:-2
Wait... and... go!

00:40:48.960 --> 00:40:51.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Dynamic duo.</c>
Yeah. Get her on to the bank there.

00:41:00.960 --> 00:41:01.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>Good job, Doc.</c>

00:41:01.960 --> 00:41:03.960 align:middle line:-3
Yeah, well,
she's not out of the woods yet.

00:41:03.960 --> 00:41:06.960 align:middle line:-3
She's had a myasthenic crisis.
That means that all the muscles

00:41:06.960 --> 00:41:08.960 align:middle line:-3
associated with breathing
have stopped.

00:41:08.960 --> 00:41:10.960 align:middle line:-2
PHONE RINGS

00:41:10.960 --> 00:41:12.960 align:middle line:-2
Oh, here. You keep squeezing.

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:15.960 align:middle line:-2
Louisa?

00:41:15.960 --> 00:41:18.800 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Oh, Martin. What's happening?</c>

00:41:18.800 --> 00:41:20.960 align:middle line:-3
She's fine. She almost
drove off a cliff, though.

00:41:20.960 --> 00:41:22.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>What?</c>

00:41:22.960 --> 00:41:24.960 align:middle line:-3
Yeah, an ambulance is on its way.
She's all right.

00:41:24.960 --> 00:41:25.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>'Thank God.'</c>

00:41:25.960 --> 00:41:28.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Er, I should make sure</c>
<c.cyan>Dylan's all right.</c>

00:41:28.960 --> 00:41:31.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>'Well, you better get a move on,</c>
<c.cyan>or you'll miss Professor Langan.'</c>

00:41:31.960 --> 00:41:33.960 align:middle line:-3
Yes, I know. I'll get there
as quick as I can.

00:41:33.960 --> 00:41:35.960 align:middle line:-3
CAR CREAKS
Bye.

00:41:37.960 --> 00:41:41.960 align:middle line:-2
CRASHING

00:41:43.960 --> 00:41:45.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Look, he said he's on his way.</c>

00:41:45.960 --> 00:41:47.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>If it was that important to him,</c>
<c.green>he'd already be here.</c>

00:41:47.960 --> 00:41:49.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>You're very loyal, Christopher.</c>

00:41:49.960 --> 00:41:52.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>That's not always a good thing.</c>
<c.yellow>Hello.</c>

00:41:52.960 --> 00:41:55.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I have collected</c>
<c.yellow>over 5,000 signatures</c>

00:41:55.960 --> 00:41:58.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>demanding the reinstatement</c>
<c.yellow>of Dr Martin Ellingham.</c>

00:41:58.960 --> 00:42:00.800 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Did you write all these?</c>

00:42:00.800 --> 00:42:02.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>That's a very serious accusation.</c>

00:42:02.960 --> 00:42:05.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>It wouldn't matter anyway,</c>
<c.green>it's not a popularity contest.</c>

00:42:05.960 --> 00:42:08.000 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>But you have to wait</c>
<c.yellow>to see the doctor.</c>

00:42:08.000 --> 00:42:10.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I'm sorry, who are you?</c>
<c.cyan>I think she's the local chemist.</c>

00:42:10.960 --> 00:42:13.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>No, I'm a licensed pharmacist</c>
<c.yellow>and a concerned citizen.</c>

00:42:13.960 --> 00:42:15.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>What are you doing?</c>
<c.cyan>A chemist.</c>

00:42:15.960 --> 00:42:17.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I'm not letting you leave</c>
<c.yellow>until you've seen the doctor.</c>

00:42:17.960 --> 00:42:20.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>No, no, no, don't do that!</c>

00:42:20.960 --> 00:42:22.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>What on earth is wrong with you?</c>

00:42:30.960 --> 00:42:33.320 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Doc, tell him</c>
<c.yellow>it was a learning experience.</c>

00:42:33.320 --> 00:42:36.160 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>Completely meaningless,</c>
<c.yellow>but works every time.</c>

00:42:37.960 --> 00:42:40.800 align:middle line:-3
Professor Langan.
<c.green>Ellingham.</c>

00:42:40.800 --> 00:42:41.960 align:middle line:-2
What are you doing here?

00:42:41.960 --> 00:42:44.480 align:middle line:-2
SHE MUMBLES

00:42:44.480 --> 00:42:46.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>She's got Professor Langan's</c>
<c.cyan>car keys in her mouth.</c>

00:42:46.960 --> 00:42:50.000 align:middle line:-3
SHE MUMBLES
Spit them out, right now.

00:42:50.000 --> 00:42:51.960 align:middle line:-3
SHE GROANS
Now!

00:42:53.960 --> 00:42:56.960 align:middle line:-3
Go away.
<c.yellow>What if you need moral support?</c>

00:42:56.960 --> 00:42:58.320 align:middle line:-2
I don't. Thank you. Go away.

00:43:01.960 --> 00:43:02.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Thank you.</c>

00:43:02.960 --> 00:43:05.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Martin, you...</c>
<c.cyan>you wanted to say something?</c>

00:43:05.960 --> 00:43:08.960 align:middle line:-2
Yes. Er, I'd like to practise again,

00:43:08.960 --> 00:43:11.960 align:middle line:-3
and I'm aware that it's appropriate
that I apologise for what happened.

00:43:11.960 --> 00:43:13.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Go on.</c>

00:43:13.960 --> 00:43:15.960 align:middle line:-3
Well, to be perfectly honest,
I'm not entirely clear

00:43:15.960 --> 00:43:18.480 align:middle line:-3
exactly what it is I'm supposed to
be apologising for,

00:43:18.480 --> 00:43:20.960 align:middle line:-3
but I do confess
that I made a mistake

00:43:20.960 --> 00:43:23.000 align:middle line:-2
when I resigned from medicine.

00:43:23.000 --> 00:43:24.960 align:middle line:-2
I was surprised, though,

00:43:24.960 --> 00:43:26.960 align:middle line:-3
at your readiness
to accept that resignation.

00:43:26.960 --> 00:43:28.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>So it's my fault? Right!</c>

00:43:28.960 --> 00:43:30.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Nice to see you again, Ellingham.</c>

00:43:30.960 --> 00:43:33.320 align:middle line:-3
Professor Langan,
the reason I'm late is...

00:43:33.320 --> 00:43:35.960 align:middle line:-3
I just performed an intubation
on a patient suffering

00:43:35.960 --> 00:43:38.960 align:middle line:-3
a myasthenic crisis while her car
was perched on the edge of a cliff.

00:43:38.960 --> 00:43:40.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>No, no, no, no, you didn't, Martin.</c>

00:43:40.960 --> 00:43:42.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Because that would be very bad.</c>

00:43:42.960 --> 00:43:45.640 align:middle line:-3
There is a policeman here
who can verify those facts.

00:43:45.640 --> 00:43:47.960 align:middle line:-3
If you don't reinstate me,
I must insist

00:43:47.960 --> 00:43:50.960 align:middle line:-3
that you have me arrested for
practising without a licence,

00:43:50.960 --> 00:43:52.960 align:middle line:-3
under the outlines
of The Medical Act of 1983.

00:43:52.960 --> 00:43:55.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Are you giving me an ultimatum?</c>

00:43:55.960 --> 00:43:56.960 align:middle line:-2
No, I'm giving you a promise.

00:43:56.960 --> 00:43:59.640 align:middle line:-3
If I hadn't acted,
that woman would have died.

00:43:59.640 --> 00:44:00.960 align:middle line:-3
So I will continue to treat
my patients

00:44:00.960 --> 00:44:02.960 align:middle line:-2
and do the best I can for them,

00:44:02.960 --> 00:44:05.960 align:middle line:-3
regardless
of the consequences to myself.

00:44:07.960 --> 00:44:11.960 align:middle line:-3
Also...
it's been a learning experience.

00:44:16.960 --> 00:44:17.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>Fine.</c>

00:44:19.960 --> 00:44:21.960 align:middle line:-2
Fine?

00:44:22.960 --> 00:44:25.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>You're a good doctor</c>
<c.green>and we need good doctors.</c>

00:44:25.960 --> 00:44:27.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.green>There'll be paperwork to shuffle</c>

00:44:27.960 --> 00:44:30.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>and a written retraction</c>
<c.green>of resignation will be required,</c>

00:44:30.960 --> 00:44:34.800 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>then an appraisal - but as you said,</c>
<c.green>you've learned from this.</c>

00:44:34.800 --> 00:44:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>And maybe that's</c>
<c.green>the most important thing of all.</c>

00:44:40.640 --> 00:44:43.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>I will recommend to the GMC</c>
<c.green>that you are relicensed.</c>

00:44:43.960 --> 00:44:45.480 align:middle line:-2
Thank you, sir.

00:44:50.960 --> 00:44:53.960 align:middle line:-3
So what happens now?
<c.cyan>What do you mean "what happens now"?</c>

00:44:53.960 --> 00:44:57.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>You've got what you wanted,</c>
<c.cyan>you're a doctor again.</c>

00:44:57.640 --> 00:45:00.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I mean, don't think you need</c>
<c.cyan>to thank me or anything. </c>Hmm.

00:45:00.960 --> 00:45:02.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>I mean, you can, if you want to.</c>

00:45:02.960 --> 00:45:06.640 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>I did put my reputation</c>
<c.cyan>on the line for you.</c>

00:45:06.640 --> 00:45:09.320 align:middle line:-2
Yes. You're right.

00:45:11.960 --> 00:45:13.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.cyan>Welcome back, Martin.</c>

00:45:19.960 --> 00:45:22.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>My last job was</c>
<c.yellow>a hotel receptionist.</c>

00:45:22.960 --> 00:45:24.960 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>This is probably way easier, though.</c>

00:45:24.960 --> 00:45:27.640 align:middle line:-3
So, is the doc up for moving, then?
<c.cyan>We're just looking. That's all.</c>

00:45:27.640 --> 00:45:29.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.green>Louisa has her heart set</c>
<c.green>on West Cliff House.</c>

00:45:29.960 --> 00:45:30.960 align:middle line:-2
This house isn't for sale.

00:45:30.960 --> 00:45:33.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.yellow>I gave her 40 years of my life.</c>
<c.yellow>You'd think that would be enough.</c>

00:45:33.960 --> 00:45:36.960 align:middle line:-3
<c.cyan>Winnie's... dead, though.</c>
<c.yellow>What you doing here?!</c>

00:45:36.960 --> 00:45:38.960 align:middle line:-2
Just put the jug down, please.

00:45:38.960 --> 00:45:40.480 align:middle line:-2
<c.yellow>This is not what it seems, Doc.</c>

00:45:40.480 --> 00:45:42.960 align:middle line:-2
